io.odysz.semantic.jsession

Class JUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.odysz.anson.Anson
      • io.odysz.semantics.SemanticObject
        • io.odysz.semantic.jsession.JUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.odysz.anson.IJsonable, io.odysz.semantics.IUser

    public class JUser
extends io.odysz.semantics.SemanticObject
implements io.odysz.semantics.IUser

    IUser implementation supporting session.

    This object is usually created when user logged in, and is used for semantics processing like finger print, etc.

    The logging connection is configured in configs.xml/k=log-connId.

    A subclass can be used for handling serv without login.

    Author:
    odys-z@github.com
